;B[ps]LB[rs:1][ps:2][ss:A]C[Dia.2 Lives in double pae

White 1 would be the next move and  then Black will take at 2.  Notice how White cannot connect at A, that'll let Black live.  If White finds a pae threat it doesn't matter.  Taking Black 2 will only result in Black taking at A.  Black lives in double pae.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

