;W[rr]LB[or:1][pr:2][rr:3][or:A][qr:C][os:B][rs:A]C[Dia.3 Correct/ Start with Dansu

You should first play the dansu of White 1.  Then, White should make an eye in the corner with A.  If Black plays at A, no problem, White will play at B.  If Black B, White C.  There's nothing Black can do.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

